    b"search.SearchDepthDecision\x00\x00\x01\x00w\x13\x00\x00\x0a        {{ _.role(\"system\") }}\x0a\x0a        Choos"
    b"e timestamp cutoffs for each listed search domain. Your job is to quickly decide"
    b" an appropriate cutoff date based on current context.\x0a\x0a        Stop once you hav"
    b"e timestamps that look good enough for the request without thinking about it too"
    b" much.\x0a\x0a        Rules:\x0a        - Return a SearchDepthDecision with depths and op"
